Update Using Dataloader.io
download account-site file by clicking (clicking here)
contents of the "Account Site" column from the "account-site file" into the blank "Site" column in the "Accounts Export" file
==================================================================================================================================================================================
Windows users:

Accounts Export.csv file --> File --> Save As --> file type CSV (Comma delimited) (*.csv) --> filename : Updated Account Site Import --> Save.
==================================================================================================================================================================================
Dataloader.io --> NEW TASK --> IMPORT --> Update --> Object : Account --> Next --> Upload CSV --> File : Updated Account Site Import --> Open --> Next --> Save & Run --> Run
==================================================================================================================================================================================
View the Results
App Launcher --> Sales --> Accounts  --> List View Controls icon --> New --> List Name: Accounts Modified Today --> Only I can see this list view (checked) --> Save --> Add Filter
                                    Field                   Operator          Value
                                    Last Modified Date      equals            TODAY
--> Done --> Add Filter
                                    Field           Operator          Value
                                    Account Site	  not equal to      (leave this value blank)
--> Done --> Save
